  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety Trial of ALK-depot SQ Mites in Subjects With Atopic Dermatitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Parallel Group Study to Demonstrate the Efficacy of a 12-month Subcutaneous Specific Immunotherapy With ALK-depot SQ Milbenmischung in Patients With Atopic Dermatitis and Proven IgE-mediated Sensitization to House Dust Mites</official_title>
